headline: Medtronic to announce financial results for its third quarter of fiscal year 2026
summary: Medtronic plc (NYSE: MDT), a global leader in healthcare technology, today announced that it will report financial results on Tuesday, February 17, 2026, for its third quarter of fiscal year 2026, which ended on Friday, January 23, 2026.
